root: ^Player: It's not quite what I expected.
^Player: Im not going to complain. I can already feel my body failing me.
^Voice: I told you what was going to happen, but you refused to heed my words.
^Player: I don't regret it, I think this is quite a good ending for me. All stories are bound to end someday, and it so happens to be mine today.
^Voice: If you say so, see you on the other side.
